duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide patient care in medical-surgical settings, including assessment, medication administration, and wound care.
Collaborate with healthcare team members to develop and implement patient care plans.
Utilize EMR systems to accurately document patient information and treatment plans.
Demonstrate clinical knowledge and critical thinking to provide safe and effective patient care.
Adapt to fast-paced and dynamic healthcare environments, prioritizing time management and handling multiple patient cases.
Show compassion and empathy towards patients and their families, providing emotional support and comfort.
